这是你的新手机卡
Here is your new sim card.

196
00:19:54,680 --> 00:19:55,730
把东西放屋里去
Keep the stuff inside

197
00:20:07,360 --> 00:20:08,860
你要换手机号吗?
You changing you number?

198
00:20:09,700 --> 00:20:12,950
你是律师吗? 问东问西的
Are you a lawyer? Every time asking me questions.

199
00:20:13,990 --> 00:20:15,940
我要回村里呆几天
I will be going to my village for some days.

200
00:20:15,950 --> 00:20:17,080
要是有人问起 你就告诉他们
If any one ask just inform them.

201
00:20:18,920 --> 00:20:20,340
行了 你可以走了
Now, go away from here.

202
00:20:33,230 --> 00:20:35,520
带我一起去吧
Take me along with you.

203
00:20:36,860 --> 00:20:41,440
我要去那里办事 不是去旅游
I'm going for my work not to have fun.

204
00:20:42,110 --> 00:20:45,150
我很快就回来
I will be back fast.

205
00:20:46,370 --> 00:20:49,250
在我回来以前... 
And untill then ... 

206
00:20:49,250 --> 00:20:52,140
不要和任何人提及此事
Do not tell anyone anything.

207
00:20:56,590 --> 00:20:59,270
他为什么去西普利斯路?
What was he doing at Sipleas Road?

208
00:20:59,800 --> 00:21:02,080
