Tell us some intrested news about it.

210
00:21:04,810 --> 00:21:06,440
没有什么 只是普通的车祸而已
Nothing much, it was just an accident.

211
00:21:07,230 --> 00:21:08,860
可以把水递给我吗?
Can I have water please?

212
00:21:08,980 --> 00:21:10,730
你见到索尼娅·卡普尔了吗?
Did you meet Sonia Kapoor?

213
00:21:11,190 --> 00:21:13,320
她本人漂亮吗?
Does she look preety in real life?

214
00:21:17,600 --> 00:21:21,000
太可惜了 他还年轻 不是吗? 
So sad, he was very young right? 

215
00:21:22,190 --> 00:21:23,270
不应该死得这么早
He should not die.

216
00:21:23,330 --> 00:21:25,410
