Thousands of people die in young age everyday.

217
00:21:26,120 --> 00:21:27,710
倒是没有人为他们感到忧伤
Nobody says anything then.

218
00:21:35,960 --> 00:21:37,130
抱歉!
Sorry!

219
00:21:37,760 --> 00:21:39,830
我的朋友 你在说什么呢? 
My friend what are you talking? 

220
00:21:39,830 --> 00:21:41,600
没什么抱歉的 不是吗?
Why must you apologize to us?

221
00:21:43,640 --> 00:21:45,050
她现在感觉如何?
How is she now?

222
00:21:45,060 --> 00:21:48,150
比之前好很多
Better than last time.

223
00:21:48,640 --> 00:21:51,970
我和心理医师安贾利·庞加比谈过
I have spoke to a psychiatric Anjali Punjabi.

224
00:21:51,980 --> 00:21:53,700
嗯 她相当厉害
Yes she is quit good.

225
00:21:54,190 --> 00:21:57,360
嗯 罗西尼也如此
Ya, I think the same for Roshini.

226
00:22:03,450 --> 00:22:04,160
还需要其他什么吗?
Do you need anything?

227
00:22:05,120 --> 00:22:06,000
不 谢谢
No, thanks.

228
00:23:06,980 --> 00:23:08,610
