Yes sir, there was nothing found 

236
00:23:47,910 --> 00:23:49,600
没有任何关于酒精中毒的信息
in his post mortem report of any toxication.

237
00:23:49,850 --> 00:23:52,440
他的肺部积水过多 导致他溺水身亡
His lungs was full with water and he died of drawning.

238
00:23:52,650 --> 00:23:53,400
长官
Sir.

239
00:23:53,860 --> 00:23:57,450
我觉得这个案件没有办法结案 一切都说不通
I feel this going to be unsolve case, nothing is making sense.

240
00:24:09,960 --> 00:24:11,080
走吧
Come on.

241
00:24:11,540 --> 00:24:15,800
成千上万的来宾参加了宝莱坞影星
Thousands of people attended the burial 

242
00:24:15,800 --> 00:24:18,630
