of Bollywood star Armaan Kapoor.

243
00:24:30,100 --> 00:24:33,650
你好 我是弗拉尼 我住在这里附近 
Hello,I'm Frani.I stay in this colony 

244
00:24:33,650 --> 00:24:35,320
