No, thank you.

249
00:24:44,450 --> 00:24:47,070
没有什么需要帮忙的 就是收拾东西罢了
I'm ok. Just just neede to do some unpacking.

250
00:24:47,080 --> 00:24:49,250
如果需要帮忙的话 打电话给我就行了
If you need any help just call for me.

251
00:24:49,670 --> 00:24:51,070
我是号码百事通 
I have everyone's phone number:

252
00:24:51,070 --> 00:24:52,840
木匠 电工 水管工 
carpenter, electriction, plumber 

253
00:24:52,840 --> 00:24:55,300
这些人的号码我应有尽有...
and...

254
00:24:56,840 --> 00:24:57,930
谢谢你
Thank you.

255
00:25:02,260 --> 00:25:03,500
我能喝杯茶吗?
Can I have some tea?

256
00:25:03,510 --> 00:25:06,770
哦 是的 当然 你请坐
Oh yes sure, please have a sit.

257
00:25:12,480 --> 00:25:15,160
你的丈夫出门抓小偷时
Are you always alone at home

258
00:25:15,440 --> 00:25:18,370
你常常一个人在家吗?
when your husband is chasing after thives?

259
00:25:22,490 --> 00:25:24,330
你们结婚多久?
How many years have you been married?

260
00:25:24,660 --> 00:25:26,250
十二年
12 years.

261
00:26:17,630 --> 00:26:19,620
你需要加糖吗?
Do you take sugar?

262
00:26:19,640 --> 00:26:23,220
是的 亲爱的 两勺糖
Yes dear, 2 tea spoons.

263
00:26:29,270 --> 00:26:30,270
你好 卡伦
Hello Karen.

264
00:26:42,700 --> 00:26:44,040
督查 你好
Hello inspector.

265
00:26:44,160 --> 00:26:45,000
你好
Greetings.

266
00:26:45,080 --> 00:26:48,010
这位是桑杰 他是阿尔曼的儿时好友
This is Sanjay, Armaan's childhood friend.

267
00:26:49,710 --> 00:26:51,200
您请坐
Have a sit please.

268
00:26:51,210 --> 00:26:52,000
谢谢
Thank you.

269
00:26:54,840 --> 00:26:58,510
索尼娅 我们对你丈夫当晚的行踪不甚了解
Sonia,we still do not know where your husband when on that night,

270
00:26:58,880 --> 00:27:01,180
也不知道他去那里做什么
or what was he doing on that road.

271
00:27:01,390 --> 00:27:03,060
那车祸呢?
And accident?

272
00:27:03,930 --> 00:27:10,150
我们也不明白为什么他的车会转弯坠入海里
And we also can't understand why his car turn and fall into the ocean.

273
00:27:13,360 --> 00:27:17,320
索尼娅女士 我冒昧问一句
Madam Sonia,forgive me for asking

274
00:27:18,280 --> 00:27:19,110
是的
Yes.

275
00:27:19,200 --> 00:27:22,660
他是不是有什么困扰?
Was there any thing bothering him?

276
00:27:25,160 --> 00:27:27,330
我的意思是 他是不是有什么心理压力
I meant was he having probleams.

277
00:27:29,540 --> 00:27:31,790
督查 阿尔曼绝对不是自杀 
Armaan did not kill himself Inspector!

278
00:27:33,170 --> 00:27:38,220
他为什么自杀呢? 是你们没法结案 对吧?
Why will he kill himself? You guys cant solve the case, is it?

279
00:27:50,690 --> 00:27:53,450
今天早上 我的会计师告诉我
Today morning, my accountant told me

280
00:27:53,980 --> 00:27:58,240
事发当天 他给了阿尔曼 两百万卢比的现金
on that day he past Armaan Rs20 lakh cash.

281
00:28:00,380 --> 00:28:03,470
为什么?
Why?

282
00:28:05,230 --> 00:28:08,850
我是早上七点半把现金给他的
I gave him the cash at 7.30.

283
00:28:09,250 --> 00:28:12,580
你之前怎么没把这件事情告诉索尼娅?
Why didn't you tell Sonia about this?

284
00:28:12,590 --> 00:28:14,310
长官 我当时想告诉她
Sir, I tried to tell her but

285
00:28:14,760 --> 00:28:17,550
但是看她那么难过 所以我没有开口
she was in a shock,that's why I could not talk to her.

286
00:28:20,090 --> 00:28:22,300
以多大的面值给的?
What kind of notes was it?

287
00:28:22,680 --> 00:28:27,420
上千的面值 当时是装在美洲豹牌的绿色包里
In thousands, it was a green colour PUMA bag.

288
00:28:27,440 --> 00:28:29,190
我们没有找到你说的提包
We did not find such bag.

289
00:28:30,350 --> 00:28:32,400
那天晚上 你是不是偷看了他的东西?
That night you peeked his stuff right?

290
00:28:34,650 --> 00:28:35,990
快说!
Tell me!

291
00:28:36,530 --> 00:28:41,030
行李有一些音乐器材 午餐饭盒 
There were music system, lunch box 

292
00:28:42,080 --> 00:28:45,410
还有会计师给的提包
and a bag which was given by the accountant.

293
00:28:45,620 --> 00:28:46,450
是红色的吧?
Red colour right?

294
00:28:47,410 --> 00:28:48,670
不 长官 是绿色的包
No sir, it was green in colour

295
00:28:49,080 --> 00:28:50,990
包里有什么? 你打开包看里面的东西了吗?
What was in that beg? Did you open and see it?

296
00:28:51,000 --> 00:28:53,450
没有 长官 我不会不经过他的同意
No sir,I will never open his beg 

297
00:28:53,450 --> 00:28:54,830
擅自看他包里的东西
without his permission.

298
00:28:54,840 --> 00:28:55,920
真的吗?
Really?

299
00:28:56,880 --> 00:28:58,120
没错 长官
Really sir.

300
00:28:58,130 --> 00:29:00,640
他对你提起过那个包的事情吗?
Did Mr Kapoor tell anything about the bag?

301
00:29:00,760 --> 00:29:02,400
没有 长官
No sir.

302
00:29:02,640 --> 00:29:04,030
他原来这么干过吗?
Have he done this before?

303
00:29:06,770 --> 00:29:07,600
是的 有过两次.
Yes, 2 times.

304
00:29:08,060 --> 00:29:11,790
一年前 阿尔曼先生让我
1 year back Mr. Armaan did ask me 

305
00:29:11,790 --> 00:29:15,860
把一百万卢比送到里多酒店
to deliver Rs 10 lakh to Hotel Lido...

306
00:29:16,570 --> 00:29:18,610
这家酒店就位于发生车祸的那条马路
which is on the same road where his death tragic happen.

307
00:29:19,410 --> 00:29:20,280
为什么?
Why?

308
00:29:20,280 --> 00:29:25,710
我不知道 长官 他只是让我交给酒店前台
I do not know sir. I was just told to past it to the receptionist.

309
00:29:29,420 --> 00:29:32,860
你们有个员工叫安纳德·穆鲁根吧?
You had a worker by the name of Anand Murugen?

310
00:29:34,250 --> 00:29:35,300
穆鲁根...
Murugen...

311
00:29:35,510 --> 00:29:38,270
他在你们酒店前台工作了四年
For 4 years he was you hotel receptionist.

312
00:29:39,760 --> 00:29:42,480
是的 但是他辞职之后 
But he has resign 

313
00:29:42,490 --> 00:29:44,970
我们就没有他的消息了
and after that we did not hear any news.

314
00:29:45,770 --> 00:29:46,980
这是一个敲诈案件
It's extotion case.

315
00:29:47,180 --> 00:29:51,570
如果当真如此 他肯定会对别人说起
If it's extotion im sure he would have talk to somebody.

316
00:29:51,980 --> 00:29:53,960
就连他的妻子和关系好的朋友
Even his wife or any of his close friend 

317
00:29:53,960 --> 00:29:55,180
也不清楚这件事情
do not knows anything.

318
00:29:55,190 --> 00:29:57,530
