Got blackmail any relevance to his death.

319
00:29:57,900 --> 00:29:59,110
但是好像并非如此
By right it should not.

320
00:29:59,490 --> 00:30:02,030
证据很多 可是没有办法联系起来
There are many evidence whithout the right answer.

321
00:30:02,870 --> 00:30:05,080
今天早上 她的妻子要求做最终检验记录
And today his wife filed F.I.R.

322
00:30:06,200 --> 00:30:07,760
这是她唯一可以做的事情
This was the only thing left for her to do.

323
00:30:08,500 --> 00:30:10,670
出动所有警力 调查这起案件
Get all my police force to investigate for this Hero's case.

324
00:30:11,560 --> 00:30:13,750
长官 如果找到那个前台服务员
Sir,If it is found that the desk clerk.

325
00:30:13,840 --> 00:30:15,550
也许可以找到更多线索
Maybe you can find out more in detall.

326
00:30:15,590 --> 00:30:16,980
争取早日破案
So find him faster.

327
00:30:16,960 --> 00:30:18,000
是 长官
Yes,sir.

328
00:30:22,470 --> 00:30:24,600
长官 我是沙希
Sir, Shashi speeking.

329
00:30:24,850 --> 00:30:27,550
您多次给我打电话 发生什么事情?
What you want calling me so many times?

330
00:30:27,560 --> 00:30:29,600
我早已更换电话号码 长官
Had to change my phone number sir.

331
00:30:30,230 --> 00:30:31,730
最近发生一点麻烦
There is a problem going on.

332
00:30:31,940 --> 00:30:33,600
那天晚上阿尔曼发生什么事情?
What happen that night with Armaan ?

333
00:30:33,610 --> 00:30:35,820
我对此毫不知情 我当时并不在现场
I do not know anything. I was not even there.

334
00:30:37,280 --> 00:30:39,650
不要狡辩 警察已经知道两百万卢比的事情
Don't lie, police knows about the Rs 20 lakh.

335
00:30:39,660 --> 00:30:40,620
