This is my husband Suri and this is Frani our neighboor

347
00:31:45,680 --> 00:31:48,260
她和她的哥哥维莱·莫里巡官住一起
and she stays with her brother Inspector Vilai Morri.

348
00:31:48,270 --> 00:31:49,990
