Are you guys going home?

351
00:31:55,610 --> 00:31:56,190
是的
Yes.

352
00:32:00,790 --> 00:32:02,430
你还好吗 苏尔扬?
How are you Surjan?

353
00:32:05,590 --> 00:32:06,980
